Patches for this platform are sourced automatically at build time from:
  ARM64_EXTERNAL_REPO_URL (configs/kernel_versions.conf)
  → misc.cbm/patches/v<series>/mt8183*.patch
  → misc.cbm/patches/v<series>/mt81xx*.patch

Place any local device-specific overrides here as *.patch files
if you ever need something not covered by the upstream repo.
